list.abstract: boy（英 [bɔɪ]，美 [bɔɪ]），英语单词，作名词为男孩；男青年；男人。作惊叹词为好家伙。短语搭配有little boy（小男孩）。例句为“The boy held the trunk and tried to pull it out.（男孩抓住树干，想把它拔出来。）” boy相关近义词有he、guy等，相关反义词有female child、girl等。
帕克恩·查博里拉克（Pakorn Chatborirak，1984年8月20日-），别名Boy，出生于泰国，毕业于泰国朱拉隆宫大学，泰国男模特、演员。 他的主要作品有《爱在拜城》《筑梦庄园之魅力》《黄金三人组》《日耀云帘》等。

yingyinNormal.en: But he's not a boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但他不是个男孩。

yingyinNormal.en: How many bairns? A boy and two girls.
yingyinNormal.zh: 几个孩子？一个男孩两个女孩。

yingyinNormal.en: Use the boy. Come here, Potter! Now!
yingyinNormal.zh: 利用这男孩。你过来，波特，快。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, and we named the boy Jack, after Dad.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们给男孩起名叫杰克，随老爸的。

yingyinNormal.en: There was a boy. Watch. I'm going to call him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是有个男孩，看着，我要叫他过来。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, look who's out after dark, like a big boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 某人像个大男孩一样，夜游晚归哦。

yingyinNormal.en: Or in this case, the bar mitzvah boy with pinkeye.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或者就像是得了红眼病的犹太小男孩。

yingyinNormal.en: Can't we just use a pen? No, Amish boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不能够用笔就好了吗？不可以，阿们宗派男孩（17世纪成立）。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey! Here's my boy. Here's my boy. And here's his Barbie. What's my boy doing with a Barbie?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的小男孩呢？我的小男孩在这儿还有他的芭比娃娃！我儿子干嘛玩芭比娃娃？

yingyinNormal.en: Is it a girl or a boy? It's a girl. No. George does not want to be a girl baby. Ok. It's a boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是小女孩还是小男孩？是小女孩。不是，乔治并不想做一个小女孩。那好吧，是个小男孩。

yingyinNormal.en: Who's my favorite Backstreet Boy? Nice try. NSYNC forever. Damn it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我最喜欢的"后街男孩"成员是？陷阱题，永远只爱超级男孩。靠。

yingyinNormal.en: You're ready to have a baby? My boy's all grown up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们准备要怀孕了？我的小男孩长大了。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you fully grown? No. I believe he's just a boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你长成熟了吗？还没。我想他只是个男孩。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a boy. Is he okay? He's just fine. You did it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是个男孩！他不要紧吧？！不要紧的.你成功了！

yingyinNormal.en: But I didn't get to... I've seen enough. I'm a seven-year-old boy...
yingyinNormal.zh: 但我还没…我看够了。我是7岁男孩

yingyinNormal.en: So a little boy picks one up, and he throws it back into the water.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以有个小男孩捡起一只海星，把它扔回了大海。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, you too. Growing of a boy like creatures need their strength.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，你也来一片吧，一个男孩样子的生物需要能量。

yingyinNormal.en: And when a nice boy who adores you offer you pie, say thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 另外，要是有位喜欢你的男孩送你一块派，说声谢谢。

yingyinNormal.en: All right! Let's do this boy up! Check out what I got him. Bling!
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了！我们给这男孩送礼物吧！看看我送他什么礼物！

yingyinNormal.en: That's why we exist in an alternate universe to Troy the basketball boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我们和篮球男孩特洛伊生活在不同的世界里。

examination_example.sentence: The film industry still functions as a straight, white, <highlight>boy</highlight>'s club.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 电影行业仍然作为一个异性恋、白人、男孩的俱乐部运作。

examination_example.sentence: For example, only one <highlight>boy</highlight> said he would like to be president when he grows up.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，只有一个男孩说他长大后想当总统。

examination_example.sentence: One <highlight>boy</highlight> said, "I'd rather be concentrating on artistic efforts than saving the world of something."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一个男孩说：“我宁愿专注于艺术创作，也不愿拯救世界。”
